          <li>VOLUME</li>
          <li>CONDITION OF VESSEL WALL</li>
          <li>RR DELAY</li>
          <li>RF DELAY</li>
          <li>PULSE DEFICIT[HR-PULSE RATE] </li>
        </ol>
      </li>
      <li>B.P : 4 LIMB B.P OF RT UL MEASURED IN SUPINE POSITION IS ___/___
